##Notes for Week 7: 1.1 Pricing with Market Power: An Introduction

The example of air travel industry is showcase because its innovative ways for pricing. As a case for the pricing strategies of the firms that have some market power or some degree of flexibility in pricing.

The main questions for this week are:

  * Is that is this a good thing for society?
  * Are all these different pricing techniques applied by businesses because they care about their bottom line, are all these pricing techniques a good thing for, for the society?
  * Are consumers and the society in general getting better because the airline has such really interesting ways of pricing their goods?
